{"tid":647971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到有人係連登話畀咗錢入戲院睇戲就唔需要執返啲垃圾走","createTime":"2018-04-30T09:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T12:08:20.000Z","uid":143499,"like":62,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5561ead0509a27fd6a5fd3e2108a2fb4f93b9a16","tid":647971,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:36:50.000Z","msg":"你啱， 你係消費者唔執走啲垃圾又唔係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你講得出呢句已經反映你嘅公民意識低，只停留係贏国及南泡嘅級別， 即係普遍冇教養冇公民意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本人同德國人入去快餐店或者戲院都有畀錢， 不過人哋食完嘢就盡量會自己處理， 所以話普遍香港人只係僅僅好過支那人， 除咗唔會週街屙屎都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺香港快餐店，我甚少見到有人會食完執返個餐盤， 即使我中學同大學嗰陣叫朋友做只會被恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過難怪嘅，見識淺薄未受過教育係好難明白自律及基本公民意識， 德國人及日本人的行為受道德及責任規限，而普支那、南泡、腥港人只能進化到受法律規限而非自律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難怪鬼佬當你香港人等於支那人，合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffd672e1b1575cbc9c25a9756ed39099fea33e2","tid":647971,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"好多人始終擺脫唔到支那骨子裏的劣根性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4299287f982e452b00e06389f4d673bc4680ce","tid":647971,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你啱， 你係消費者唔執走啲垃圾又唔係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你講得出呢句已經反映你嘅公民意識低，只停留係贏国及南泡嘅級別， 即係普遍冇教養冇公民意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本人同德國人入去快餐店或者戲院都有畀錢， 不過人哋食完嘢就盡量會自己處理， 所以話普遍香港人只係僅僅好過支那人， 除咗唔會週街屙屎都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺香港快餐店，我甚少見到有人會食完執返個餐盤， 即使我中學同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大學嗰陣叫朋友做只會被恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過難怪嘅，見識淺薄未受過教育係好難明白自律及基本公民意識， 德國人及日本人的行為受道德及責任規限，而普支那、南泡、腥港人只能進化到受法律規限而非自律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難怪鬼佬當你香港人等於支那人，合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef188c0678b82093ff8bd542b5c1790a3ecad17e","tid":647971,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"果d新移民來"},{"pid":"a8dfeeaa5c22efdf53af9fa57636c54d2826aa73","tid":647971,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e4299287f982e452b00e06389f4d673bc4680ce","tid":647971,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你啱， 你係消費者唔執走啲垃圾又唔係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你講得出呢句已經反映你嘅公民意識低，只停留係贏国及南泡嘅級別， 即係普遍冇教養冇公民意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本人同德國人入去快餐店或者戲院都有畀錢， 不過人哋食完嘢就盡量會自己處理， 所以話普遍香港人只係僅僅好過支那人， 除咗唔會週街屙屎都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺香港快餐店，我甚少見到有人會食完執返個餐盤， 即使我中學同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大學嗰陣叫朋友做只會被恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown