018-04-30T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你啱， 你係消費者唔執走啲垃圾又唔係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你講得出呢句已經反映你嘅公民意識低，只停留係贏国及南泡嘅級別， 即係普遍冇教養冇公民意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本人同德國人入去快餐店或者戲院都有畀錢， 不過人哋食完嘢就盡量會自己處理， 所以話普遍香港人只係僅僅好過支那人， 除咗唔會週街屙屎都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺香港快餐店，我甚少見到有人會食完執返個餐盤， 即使我中學同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大學嗰陣叫朋友做只會被恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過難怪嘅，見識淺薄未受過教育係好難明白自律及基本公民意識， 德國人及日本人的行為受道德及責任規限，而普支那、南泡、腥港人只能進化到受法律規限而非自律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難怪鬼佬當你香港人等於支那人，合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"Tree U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"最好笑嘅係人哋日本小學生已經做到， 香港讀HKU都未必學習到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb11e7918e1b8c863234e4aae00c9a0bcafdef5","tid":647971,"uid":56107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09: